==反響==
瘟疫危機系列自《瘟疫危機2》開始便獲得了一定的聲名，而《瘟疫危機2》本身亦獲得不錯的評價。{{tsl|en|JayIsGames|}}給予此遊戲4.6/5分，並指出「多年來，雖然已經有類似『世界末日』的模擬遊戲，但《瘟疫危機2》是其中最好的。」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://jayisgames.com/archives/2008/07/pandemic_2.php|title=Pandemic 2|publisher=JayIsGames|author=Josh|date=2008-07-23|accessdate=2013-09-29|archive-date=2015-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150101070711/http://jayisgames.com/archives/2008/07/pandemic_2.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而[[OMGN|OMGN]]則於給予此遊戲9/10分，並指出「對於大部份人來說，此遊戲將會讓他們感到非常愉快。」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://omgn.com/review/2011/01/21/pandemic-2|title=Pandemic 2 Review|date=2011-01-21|accessdate=2013-09-29|author=Liam Reid|publisher=OMGN|archive-date=2019-09-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190916153729/http://omgn.com/review/2011/01/21/pandemic-2|dead-url=no}}</ref>。另外，下載次數超越1000萬次的戰略遊戲《[[瘟疫公司|瘟疫公司]]》的開發者詹姆斯·沃恩亦指出遊戲靈感來自《瘟疫危機2》<ref>[http://www.hookshotinc.com/cloning-vs-evolution-pandemic-mutates-into-plague-inc Cloning vs. Evolution: Pandemic mutates into Plague Inc. - Hookshot Inc. ] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121126075125/http://www.hookshotinc.com/cloning-vs-evolution-pandemic-mutates-into-plague-inc |date=2012-11-26 }}</ref>。

《瘟疫危機2.5》則獲得一般的評價。兩個匯總評分媒體[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]和[[GameRankings|GameRankings]]分別得出此遊戲的分數為67/100分<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/game/ios/pandemic-25|title=Pandemic 2.5 iOS|publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|accessdate=2013-09-29|archive-date=2020-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201208072549/https://www.metacritic.com/game/ios/pandemic-25|dead-url=no}}</ref>和68.00%<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamerankings.com/iphone/669504-pandemic-25/index.html|title=Pandemic 2.5|publisher=[[GameRankings|GameRankings]]|accessdate=2013-09-29|archive-date=2019-12-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191209013913/https://www.gamerankings.com/iphone/669504-pandemic-25/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。{{tsl|en|Touch Arcade|}}給予此遊戲3.5/5分，並指出「在《瘟疫危機2.5》推出後，我便忍不住馬上抹殺人類。」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://toucharcade.com/2012/05/07/pandemic-2-5-review/|title='Pandemic 2.5' Review - Shut Down the Borders, Close the Ports|publisher=Touch Arcade|author=Nissa Campbell|date=2012-05-07|accessdate=2013-09-29|archive-date=2020-02-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200207152955/https://toucharcade.com/2012/05/07/pandemic-2-5-review/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]則指出「《瘟疫危機2.5》是App Store上其中一個最有趣的策略遊戲」，並頒予「每日應用程式獎」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2012-05-19-app-of-the-day-pandemic-2-5|title=App of the Day: Pandemic 2.5|publisher=Eurogamer|date=2012-05-19|author=Dan Whitehead|accessdate=2013-09-29|archive-date=2019-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191206130430/https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2012-05-19-app-of-the-day-pandemic-2-5|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[Gamezebo|Gamezebo]]給予此遊戲3/5分，並指出「沒有什麼比抹殺全球人口能帶來更多的快感」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamezebo.com/games/pandemic-25/review|title=Pandemic 2.5 Review|publisher=Gamezebo|author=Josh Wittenkeller|date=2012-05-09|accessdate=2013-09-29|archive-date=2014-03-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140319105551/http://www.gamezebo.com/games/pandemic-25/review|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[Slide_To_Play|Slide To Play]]給予此遊戲2/4分，並指出「《瘟疫危機2.5》不會再席捲全國了」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.slidetoplay.com/review/pandemic-25-review/|title=Pandemic 2.5 Review|publisher=Slide To Play|date=2012-05-14|author=Brittany Vincent|accessdate=2013-09-29|archive-date=2014-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141003205249/http://www.slidetoplay.com/review/pandemic-25-review/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而[[Techday|Techday]]則給予2/5分，並指出「在致命的瘟疫殺死你之前，你已經因無聊死掉了。」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://techday.com/macguide/news/app-review-pandemic-2-5/163464/|title=App Review: Pandemic 2.5|date=2012-05-30|author=Benjamin Matthews|publisher=Techday|accessdate=2013-09-29|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131110043526/http://techday.com/macguide/news/app-review-pandemic-2-5/163464/|archivedate=2013-11-10}}</ref>。

